291
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:26,830
Sweep it cleaner.

292
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:28,470
Enough, stop watching.

293
00:16:28,470 --> 00:16:30,130
You've seen it too many times.

294
00:16:31,170 --> 00:16:32,300
I finally understand why

295
00:16:32,300 --> 00:16:35,400
Grandma Hongzhu loves watching prime-time dramas so much.

296
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:38,170
Do you think my brother will be punished this time?

297
00:16:38,170 --> 00:16:38,770
My father has always

298
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:39,500
