299
00:16:39,500 --> 00:16:41,000
to his mistakes.

300
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:43,860
He'll probably let him off the hook again this time.

301
00:16:44,970 --> 00:16:46,230
Don't worry.

302
00:16:46,770 --> 00:16:48,130
As long as we can plant

303
00:16:48,130 --> 00:16:49,970
seeds of discontent about Deng Weikang in your father's mind,

304
00:16:49,970 --> 00:16:51,870
