305
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:52,830
And let me tell you,

306
00:16:52,830 --> 00:16:54,300
from now on,

307
00:16:54,300 --> 00:16:55,570
your father's tolerance for your brother

308
00:16:55,570 --> 00:16:57,770
