318
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:10,770
Hey,

319
00:17:10,770 --> 00:17:11,700
Jiang Zhilu, where are you going?

320
00:17:11,700 --> 00:17:13,530
Scan it yourself. I...

321
00:17:13,530 --> 00:17:14,569
Come help me.

322
00:17:16,670 --> 00:17:17,670
Jiang Zhilu,

323
00:17:17,670 --> 00:17:19,800
