324
00:17:20,300 --> 00:17:22,400
The navigation is set up front.

325
00:17:24,329 --> 00:17:25,170
Here.

326
00:17:48,830 --> 00:17:50,370
You two!

327
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:51,830
What are you doing?

328
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:52,760
What's going on?

329
00:17:53,870 --> 00:17:54,970
Wait... Zhilu!

330
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,630
Let her go!

331
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:07,800
Who? Who are you?

332
00:18:22,430 --> 00:18:23,530
What are you doing?

333
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:28,230
Niu Yifei, what are you doing here?

334
00:18:28,230 --> 00:18:28,930
