335
00:18:28,930 --> 00:18:29,730
Mom!

336
00:18:31,670 --> 00:18:33,030
Mom, are you okay?

337
00:18:37,730 --> 00:18:38,430
This is ridiculous.

338
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:39,630
Are you crazy?

339
00:18:43,430 --> 00:18:44,830
Mom.

340
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:45,500
From my perspective,

341
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:48,500
