351
00:19:05,300 --> 00:19:07,100
Alright, I'm sorry.

352
00:19:07,100 --> 00:19:08,530
I was a bit impulsive.

353
00:19:08,530 --> 00:19:09,630
You can punch me back if you want.

354
00:19:09,630 --> 00:19:11,230
No need.

355
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:12,830
How's your mom doing?

356
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:14,170
She's fine, sleeping.

357
00:19:14,170 --> 00:19:16,500
Her family will come to stay with her soon.

358
00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:19,600
Today was supposed to be the third anniversary

359
00:19:19,770 --> 00:19:22,070
