378
00:19:56,770 --> 00:19:57,900
I like it,

379
00:19:57,900 --> 00:19:59,200
I love it.

380
00:19:59,200 --> 00:19:59,970
By the way,

381
00:19:59,970 --> 00:20:01,500
did you receive the money?

382
00:20:02,930 --> 00:20:04,700
My brother told me later

383
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:06,200
that Deng Weiyu saw it,

384
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:08,070
so he asked you to help.

385
00:20:08,070 --> 00:20:09,170
Thanks.

386
00:20:09,730 --> 00:20:10,770
Zhilu.

387
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:12,600
Come here.

388
00:20:12,600 --> 00:20:14,130
There are many flavors.

389
00:20:14,970 --> 00:20:15,970
Let me see.

390
00:20:16,700 --> 00:20:18,500
Would you like some tea?

391
00:20:18,500 --> 00:20:19,930
Or... anything is fine.

392
00:20:19,930 --> 00:20:21,230
Anything is fine?

393
00:20:21,230 --> 00:20:22,470
How about

394
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:24,630
sports drinks?

395
00:20:25,800 --> 00:20:27,330
Wouldn't that be too sweet?

396
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:29,100
No, that one isn't very sweet.

397
00:20:29,100 --> 00:20:30,370
You mean this one?

398
00:20:30,370 --> 00:20:31,830
This dolphin-shaped one.

399
00:20:36,370 --> 00:20:38,270
Do we have the materials for the meeting with Mr. Chen?

400
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:39,300
Are they ready?

401
00:20:39,300 --> 00:20:40,170
Everything's prepared.

402
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:40,870
Did you bring everything?

403
00:20:40,870 --> 00:20:41,830
Make sure. Yes, I've got everything.

404
00:20:41,830 --> 00:20:42,900
Good.

405
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:43,670
Go get the car first.

406
00:20:43,670 --> 00:20:44,800
We've made an appointment.

407
00:20:44,800 --> 00:20:45,600
Okay.

408
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:46,570
See you on the first floor.

409
00:20:46,570 --> 00:20:48,170
Hello, Mr. Chen.

410
00:20:48,170 --> 00:20:49,030
Yes.

411
00:20:49,030 --> 00:20:50,730
Alright, we'll be there soon.

412
00:20:50,730 --> 00:20:52,470
Good.

413
00:20:52,470 --> 00:20:53,330
Jinghan.

414
00:20:53,730 --> 00:20:54,470
I need to talk to you.

415
00:20:54,470 --> 00:20:56,000
Please let me explain.

416
00:20:58,330 --> 00:21:00,070
I was wrong about Li Peizhen.

417
00:21:01,530 --> 00:21:02,800
I've made up my mind.

418
00:21:05,170 --> 00:21:06,270
Let's get married.

419
00:21:06,270 --> 00:21:08,000
I want to spend my life with you.

420
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,000
Don't you like Bali?

421
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,430
We can honeymoon there.

422
00:21:11,800 --> 00:21:12,530
What do you say?

423
00:21:12,530 --> 00:21:14,460
We'll have a grand wedding in Bali.

424
00:21:14,930 --> 00:21:17,030
You'll look beautiful in a wedding dress.

425
00:21:17,030 --> 00:21:18,170
Will you marry me?

426
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:24,530
You said before you didn't want to make our relationship public.

427
00:21:24,530 --> 00:21:27,460
You said it would be inconvenient for Weijie to know.

428
00:21:28,170 --> 00:21:29,870
I believed you.

429
00:21:31,070 --> 00:21:33,270
I thought you just weren't ready yet.

430
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:36,000
That you weren't sure about your feelings for me.

431
00:21:36,870 --> 00:21:38,870
You're two-timing now!

432
00:21:38,870 --> 00:21:40,630
Have you ever considered my feelings?

433
00:21:40,630 --> 00:21:41,830
I was wrong about this.

434
00:21:41,830 --> 00:21:43,730
I'll apologize any way you want

435
00:21:43,730 --> 00:21:44,800
but I can't lose you.

436
00:21:44,800 --> 00:21:47,300
Is it me you can't lose, or my background?

437
00:22:35,870 --> 00:22:37,230
Mom.

438
00:22:37,230 --> 00:22:38,830
Aren't you having breakfast?

439
00:22:38,830 --> 00:22:41,290
You go ahead and eat. I'm going to the market.

440
00:22:44,730 --> 00:22:46,430
Leaving so early?

441
00:22:46,430 --> 00:22:47,500
Yes.

442
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:49,270
Liying.

443
00:22:49,270 --> 00:22:52,270
Don't you think your mom's been acting strange lately?

444
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:54,070
She was just singing.

445
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,430
It's not just that.

446
00:22:55,430 --> 00:22:56,770
Yesterday at dinner,

447
00:22:56,770 --> 00:22:59,000
I complained her stir-fried cabbage was too salty,

448
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,170
and not only did she not argue,

449
00:23:00,170 --> 00:23:02,300
she even poured me a glass of water.

450
00:23:02,800 --> 00:23:03,730
And also,

451
00:23:03,730 --> 00:23:04,700
this morning,

452
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:06,370
I sent a good morning picture to my friend,

453
00:23:06,370 --> 00:23:08,600
but accidentally sent it to her instead,

454
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:09,730
and guess what,

455
00:23:10,170 --> 00:23:11,930
she replied with a heart emoji.

456
00:23:12,470 --> 00:23:13,570
See?

457
00:23:17,900 --> 00:23:19,070
It's so scary.

458
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,870
Don't you think you should check on your mom?

459
00:23:33,030 --> 00:23:34,230
Hello, Mr. Huang.

460
00:23:34,230 --> 00:23:35,430
Long time no see.

461
00:23:35,430 --> 00:23:36,370
It's been a while.

462
00:23:36,370 --> 00:23:37,730
Chucky,

463
00:23:37,730 --> 00:23:39,770
do you remember me?

464
00:23:39,770 --> 00:23:41,470
Come,

465
00:23:42,170 --> 00:23:44,270
do you recognize me?

466
00:23:44,270 --> 00:23:45,630
I brought you some delicious snacks today.

467
00:23:45,630 --> 00:23:47,200
Got treats for you.

468
00:23:47,200 --> 00:23:49,070
Look. Come here.

469
00:23:50,000 --> 00:23:51,700
Tasty treats.

470
00:23:53,800 --> 00:23:54,770
What are you doing?

471
00:23:54,770 --> 00:23:55,430
What's going on?

472
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:56,130
Here,

473
00:23:57,770 --> 00:23:59,070
