474
00:23:59,070 --> 00:23:59,770
Stand up.

475
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:03,400
Great!

476
00:24:03,400 --> 00:24:04,770
So well-behaved.

477
00:24:05,930 --> 00:24:07,170
So greedy.

478
00:24:07,170 --> 00:24:08,430
Who's that guy?

479
00:24:08,430 --> 00:24:09,530
So cute.

480
00:24:09,530 --> 00:24:10,470
I don't know. How about another one?

481
00:24:10,470 --> 00:24:11,570
I want more.

482
00:24:11,570 --> 00:24:13,900
Stand up.

483
00:24:13,900 --> 00:24:14,730
That's good.

484
00:24:14,730 --> 00:24:15,730
Let it move around a bit.

485
00:24:15,730 --> 00:24:17,100
It won't get depressed. Right.

486
00:24:17,100 --> 00:24:18,230
Just like people.

487
00:24:33,230 --> 00:24:34,470
Hello.

488
00:24:34,470 --> 00:24:36,230
How may I help you?

489
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:38,460
Please have a seat.

490
00:24:43,600 --> 00:24:45,900
Do you need any legal assistance?

491
00:24:46,470 --> 00:24:47,900
I was wondering...

492
00:24:47,900 --> 00:24:49,370
I'd like to ask,

493
00:24:49,370 --> 00:24:51,170
if I want to...

494
00:24:51,170 --> 00:24:52,400
file for divorce.

495
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,630
Divorce?

496
00:24:54,370 --> 00:24:55,370
Are you currently living with your husband?

497
00:24:55,370 --> 00:24:56,730
Are you still together?

498
00:25:06,630 --> 00:25:08,000
Mom.

499
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,530
I never thought you were this kind of woman.

500
00:25:16,530 --> 00:25:18,300
I didn't have an affair.

501
00:25:18,300 --> 00:25:20,770
Much less destroy someone else's family.

502
00:25:20,770 --> 00:25:23,530
Mr. Huang's wife passed away a long time ago.

503
00:25:24,570 --> 00:25:27,500
His wife died, but your husband is still alive!

504
00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:31,200
Who knows where Guangsheng is suffering right now.

505
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:32,530
How could you want to divorce him

506
00:25:32,530 --> 00:25:34,000
for another man?

507
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:36,370
How can you face Guangsheng?

508
00:25:38,970 --> 00:25:40,200
I've already told you,

509
00:25:40,200 --> 00:25:42,930
I don't like Mr. Huang.

510
00:25:42,930 --> 00:25:46,070
I like the dog he keeps at his house.

511
00:25:46,970 --> 00:25:47,770
For a dog?

512
00:25:47,770 --> 00:25:49,230
Why get divorced?

513
00:25:49,230 --> 00:25:51,130
Are you planning to marry the dog?

514
00:25:53,170 --> 00:25:55,500
I've wanted a divorce for a long time.

515
00:26:05,930 --> 00:26:07,870
Five years.

516
00:26:07,870 --> 00:26:10,900
I've been waiting for Lin Guangsheng for five years.

517
00:26:10,900 --> 00:26:13,030
If it weren't for him,

518
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:15,530
would we be struggling so much now?

519
00:26:17,570 --> 00:26:20,770
I believe I've done everything I could for him.

520
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:28,870
When he left here,

521
00:26:28,870 --> 00:26:29,970
he left this

522
00:26:29,970 --> 00:26:32,730
