523
00:26:33,600 --> 00:26:35,670
What does this mean?

524
00:26:35,670 --> 00:26:38,000
He wanted to set me free.

525
00:26:45,130 --> 00:26:46,730
I know.

526
00:26:47,770 --> 00:26:49,630
Married couples

527
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:52,270
should share both good and bad times.

528
00:26:52,270 --> 00:26:55,000
Yes, I admit it.

529
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,670
Guangsheng was really good to me.

530
00:26:56,670 --> 00:26:59,030
He treated me well when he was making money.

531
00:26:59,030 --> 00:27:00,670
I shouldn't leave him

532
00:27:00,670 --> 00:27:02,470
