533
00:27:02,470 --> 00:27:04,430
But it's been so many years.

534
00:27:04,430 --> 00:27:06,570
Where has he been hiding?

535
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:09,470
Has he ever cared about my feelings?

536
00:27:09,470 --> 00:27:10,900
Does he know

537
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:11,900
that for his sake,

538
00:27:11,900 --> 00:27:14,270
I've begged many creditors

539
00:27:14,270 --> 00:27:16,830
not to come after me for the debts?

540
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:17,500
No matter what,

541
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:18,170
I will find a way.

542
00:27:18,170 --> 00:27:19,130
I'll do whatever it takes.

543
00:27:19,130 --> 00:27:20,600
Even if I get divorced,

544
00:27:20,600 --> 00:27:23,470
I'll find a way to take on all these debts.

545
00:27:34,630 --> 00:27:36,330
I just want

546
00:27:36,330 --> 00:27:39,470
to live my own life properly.

547
00:27:39,470 --> 00:27:41,230
