548
00:27:50,970 --> 00:27:52,100
Mom.

549
00:29:56,570 --> 00:29:58,700
Have you thought about this question?

550
00:29:59,930 --> 00:30:02,590
If our parents divorce, who would you stay with?

551
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:11,100
I'm not really asking you.

552
00:30:11,100 --> 00:30:12,830
My mind is just a mess.

553
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,800
I've actually looked into this.

554
00:30:24,430 --> 00:30:25,530
The adoption relationship

555
00:30:25,530 --> 00:30:27,700
is established separately with each adoptive parent.

556
00:30:27,700 --> 00:30:29,730
So even if they divorce,

557
00:30:29,730 --> 00:30:31,330
as long as they don't terminate the adoption,

558
00:30:31,330 --> 00:30:33,170
I'll still be their child.

559
00:30:34,130 --> 00:30:36,030
Look at how lazy my parents are.

560
00:30:36,030 --> 00:30:37,500
They wouldn't divorce

561
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:39,300
and specifically abandon me, right?

562
00:30:39,300 --> 00:30:40,200
Don't you think?

563
00:30:40,200 --> 00:30:41,370
After all,

564
00:30:41,370 --> 00:30:43,770
I'm cuter than Jiang Zhilu,

565
00:30:43,770 --> 00:30:45,000
more likable,

566
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:46,230
right?

567
00:30:47,730 --> 00:30:50,230
Jiang Zhilu is on her way here with a knife.

568
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:52,330
Run!

569
00:31:07,030 --> 00:31:08,070
What about you?

570
00:31:08,630 --> 00:31:10,690
Have you decided who you'd stay with?

571
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:17,800
I don't know.

572
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:21,100
I don't even dare to think about it.

573
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:25,200
It hurts just thinking about them separating.

574
00:31:28,170 --> 00:31:30,470
I felt so happy when I was little.

575
00:31:31,630 --> 00:31:33,630
My parents bickered a lot,

576
00:31:33,630 --> 00:31:35,830
and Grandma said mean things.

577
00:31:36,930 --> 00:31:37,900
But we all knew

578
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:40,300
that we cared deeply about each other.

579
00:31:45,670 --> 00:31:46,970
So my mom has been

580
00:31:46,970 --> 00:31:48,930
unhappy for so long.

581
00:31:50,370 --> 00:31:53,100
I'm the only one who thought nothing had changed.

582
00:32:02,130 --> 00:32:03,200
Ding.

583
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,200
Hey, Ding.

584
00:32:07,200 --> 00:32:08,500
What's wrong?

585
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:13,070
What do you mean?

586
00:32:17,230 --> 00:32:18,570
Okay, I got it.

587
00:32:19,230 --> 00:32:20,400
What happened?

588
00:32:23,770 --> 00:32:25,700
They might have found my dad.

589
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:45,170
Why are you changing the light bulb yourself?

590
00:32:45,170 --> 00:32:46,900
Aren't you afraid of falling?

591
00:32:46,900 --> 00:32:48,800
Be careful.

592
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:54,630
When you first married into this family,

593
00:32:54,630 --> 00:32:56,800
you were treated like a princess.

594
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:59,600
Guangsheng wouldn't even let you touch a dish,

595
00:32:59,600 --> 00:33:01,430
let alone change a light bulb.

596
00:33:05,170 --> 00:33:08,300
When you encounter something, you have to learn from it.

597
00:33:19,870 --> 00:33:23,200
If you really prefer that dog,

598
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,730
then go ahead.

599
00:33:25,430 --> 00:33:27,300
I won't go there anymore.

600
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:31,200
Brother Huang and Chucky

601
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,330
are moving to Hualien next week.

602
00:33:38,270 --> 00:33:40,270
So that dog's name is Chucky?

603
00:33:43,700 --> 00:33:45,570
Mom, Grandma, I'm home!

604
00:33:45,570 --> 00:33:46,570
Welcome back.

605
00:33:46,570 --> 00:33:47,800
Do you have work tomorrow?

606
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,570
If you're free,

607
00:33:48,570 --> 00:33:50,470
could you take me to the supermarket?

608
00:33:50,470 --> 00:33:51,800
Tomorrow I need to go...

609
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:54,000
Where are you going?

610
00:33:55,230 --> 00:33:57,230
Camping.

611
00:33:57,230 --> 00:33:58,230
Camping?

612
00:33:59,270 --> 00:34:00,930
Why so sudden?

613
00:34:01,430 --> 00:34:02,630
With whom?

614
00:34:03,170 --> 00:34:04,630
My classmates invited me.

615
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:07,770
Is it that chubby Yiting?

616
00:34:07,770 --> 00:34:08,500
Yiting?

617
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:09,730
No, no.

618
00:34:09,730 --> 00:34:10,830
It's Yuting.

619
00:34:10,830 --> 00:34:12,300
She's tall and slim now.

620
00:34:12,330 --> 00:34:13,900
Oh, Yuting.

621
00:34:13,900 --> 00:34:15,429
You have such a good memory.

622
00:34:19,130 --> 00:34:20,100
Are you two getting along?

623
00:34:20,100 --> 00:34:21,300
We've made up.

624
00:34:40,429 --> 00:34:41,500
Wait.

625
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:42,969
I have something for you.

626
00:34:42,969 --> 00:34:44,170
Wait. What is it?

627
00:34:44,170 --> 00:34:46,230
Here, take these snacks with you.

628
00:34:46,230 --> 00:34:48,130
You can eat them whenever you want.

629
00:34:48,130 --> 00:34:49,270
Thanks, Mom. Take this opportunity

630
00:34:49,270 --> 00:34:51,230
to relax and clear your mind.

631
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:52,030
Okay.

632
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:54,230
Aren't you going camping?

633
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:55,760
Where's your sleeping bag?

634
00:34:56,170 --> 00:35:01,000
I... I sleep...

635
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:07,000
You borrow my sleeping bag and expect me to bring it to you.

636
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,270
Such a diva.

637
00:35:08,270 --> 00:35:10,000
The sleeping bag is over there.

638
00:35:11,400 --> 00:35:12,830
Get in, I'll drive you.

639
00:35:12,830 --> 00:35:13,430
Mrs. Xueqing.

640
00:35:13,430 --> 00:35:14,430
Okay.

641
00:35:14,430 --> 00:35:15,570
Bye-bye.

642
00:35:15,570 --> 00:35:16,470
Mom, bye.

643
00:35:16,470 --> 00:35:17,100
Bye-bye.

644
00:35:17,100 --> 00:35:18,070
Bye-bye.

645
00:35:19,070 --> 00:35:19,900
Let's go.

646
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:21,030
Be careful.

647
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:22,130
Okay.

648
00:35:24,070 --> 00:35:26,130
Why is it Zhihao?

649
00:35:26,130 --> 00:35:28,430
Didn't she say she was going with Yuting?

650
00:35:43,500 --> 00:35:44,430
Lin Liying.

651
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:45,870
There's motion sickness medicine there.

652
00:35:45,870 --> 00:35:47,100
Take some.

653
00:35:51,130 --> 00:35:52,400
How thoughtful.

654
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:54,670
What new pickup technique is this?

655
00:35:54,670 --> 00:35:56,270
Are you a girl to be picked up?

656
00:36:01,000 --> 00:36:03,330
You didn't tell your mom and them.

657
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:07,430
I want to find my dad first,

658
00:36:07,430 --> 00:36:10,030
then tell my mom and grandma.

659
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:12,930
Otherwise, having hope

660
00:36:12,930 --> 00:36:14,670
and then being disappointed

661
00:36:14,670 --> 00:36:16,530
isn't that torture?

662
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:19,300
I guess you're right.

663
00:36:24,900 --> 00:36:26,970
You can stop at that intersection ahead.

664
00:36:26,970 --> 00:36:28,400
There's a bus nearby.

665
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,800
Thanks for helping me keep this from my mom.

666
00:36:39,700 --> 00:36:41,070
You missed it.

667
00:36:43,070 --> 00:36:46,130
Why take motion sickness pills for a ten-minute drive?

668
00:36:52,970 --> 00:36:54,700
You're driving far away.

669
00:36:55,870 --> 00:36:56,670
Just sit tight.

670
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:58,230
Just don't get carsick.

671
00:37:29,570 --> 00:37:30,830
Jiang Zhihao.

672
00:37:30,830 --> 00:37:32,300
I need to pee.

673
00:37:33,830 --> 00:37:35,800
Didn't you just go at the rest stop?

674
00:37:36,500 --> 00:37:38,000
I need to go again.

675
00:37:41,030 --> 00:37:42,470
How urgent is it?

676
00:37:44,970 --> 00:37:45,930
Two out of ten.

677
00:37:45,930 --> 00:37:47,100
Two?

678
00:37:49,970 --> 00:37:51,600
Are you nervous?

679
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:56,970
I've always wanted to find my dad.

680
00:37:57,870 --> 00:38:00,200
But now that we're almost there,

681
00:38:01,270 --> 00:38:03,270
I don't know what to do when I see him.

682
00:38:06,130 --> 00:38:07,300
Hey,

683
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:08,900
the engine temperature seems too high.

684
00:38:08,900 --> 00:38:10,770
What? What do you mean?

685
00:38:10,770 --> 00:38:12,630
Wait, I need to pull over.

686
00:38:12,630 --> 00:38:13,960
Let me stop for a moment.

687
00:38:20,530 --> 00:38:21,900
What's wrong?

688
00:38:28,730 --> 00:38:30,130
Is it smoking?

689
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:33,130
Let me see.

690
00:38:41,270 --> 00:38:42,730
Step back.

691
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:48,100
What are we going to do now?

692
00:38:50,200 --> 00:38:51,870
Do you have a tow truck number?

693
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:55,600
Why would you ask me that?

694
00:38:55,600 --> 00:38:57,070
We don't have much choice now.

695
00:38:57,070 --> 00:38:58,030
Let's call someone first.

696
00:38:58,030 --> 00:39:00,500
How are you going to take me there like this?

697
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,560
Maybe the tow truck can give us a ride.

698
00:39:03,030 --> 00:39:04,370
Call first. Hurry up.

699
00:39:13,430 --> 00:39:15,630
Sir, what's the problem?

700
00:39:16,370 --> 00:39:17,570
The radiator is leaking.

701
00:39:17,570 --> 00:39:19,070
The radiator is leaking.

702
00:39:19,070 --> 00:39:20,470
Will it be expensive?

703
00:39:20,470 --> 00:39:22,270
We'll need to check it first.

704
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:23,500
Thank you for your help.

705
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:24,700
Okay, no problem.

706
00:39:42,230 --> 00:39:43,200
Lin Liying.

707
00:39:43,930 --> 00:39:44,700
Would you like a cup?

708
00:39:44,700 --> 00:39:47,970
Special hand-brewed fresh coffee, two-in-one.

709
00:39:48,670 --> 00:39:50,530
You can still smell the coffee?

710
00:39:50,530 --> 00:39:52,500
All I can smell is engine oil.

711
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:55,960
If you don't want it, I'll drink it.

712
00:39:59,300 --> 00:40:00,100
Don't you think this is

713
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:03,130
a halftime break given to us by heaven?

714
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:06,400
Heaven knows you're not ready yet.

715
00:40:06,400 --> 00:40:08,500
This halftime break is quite expensive.

716
00:40:08,500 --> 00:40:10,230
The radiator is completely broken.

717
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,700
Will you help pay for it?

718
00:40:16,330 --> 00:40:17,700
I'll pay half.

719
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:19,700
Your car was already a piece of junk.

720
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:21,770
Complaining?

721
00:40:29,530 --> 00:40:30,600
Want some?

722
00:40:51,630 --> 00:40:52,600
Lin Liying.

723
00:40:54,700 --> 00:40:56,960
I don't know how your father is doing now.

724
00:40:57,570 --> 00:40:59,530
But he was framed back then.

725
00:40:59,530 --> 00:41:01,170
He was also a victim.

726
00:41:01,870 --> 00:41:03,000
Of course,

727
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:05,730
he did bribe the judges

728
00:41:05,730 --> 00:41:07,400
and was rude to Xiao Qian.

729
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,630
But regarding the toy paint issue,

730
00:41:09,630 --> 00:41:11,270
he was completely innocent.

731
00:41:12,630 --> 00:41:15,070
So I think

732
00:41:15,070 --> 00:41:18,470
you don't need to condemn him entirely

733
00:41:18,470 --> 00:41:20,400
just because someone framed him.

734
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:22,170
That's not fair to him.

735
00:41:28,470 --> 00:41:29,470
Let's listen.

736
00:41:30,170 --> 00:41:31,900
Let's hear what Xiao Qian says.

737
00:41:33,430 --> 00:41:34,600
What date?

738
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:42,800
Lin Guangsheng never liked me anyway.

739
00:41:44,270 --> 00:41:46,170
So I don't need to be nice to him.

740
00:41:47,030 --> 00:41:49,670
You need to confirm that barrel of coating was used.

741
00:41:49,670 --> 00:41:51,300
Let us know after it's been used,

742
00:41:51,300 --> 00:41:53,800
and then it's no longer your concern.

743
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:56,230
What about the conditions you promised me?

744
00:41:56,230 --> 00:41:58,230
Don't forget,

745
00:41:58,230 --> 00:42:00,890
once I get the order from Linlin Breakfast Shop,

746
00:42:00,900 --> 00:42:03,230
I won't have to worry about money anymore.

747
00:42:04,200 --> 00:42:05,530
Brother Kang said

748
00:42:05,530 --> 00:42:07,130
as long as you handle this well,

749
00:42:07,130 --> 00:42:08,770
you'll get what you deserve.

750
00:42:43,230 --> 00:42:47,330
Calling you,

751
00:42:47,330 --> 00:42:51,100
answering within three rings,

752
00:42:51,100 --> 00:42:54,170
chance meeting at a coffee shop,

753
00:42:54,170 --> 00:42:57,730
they say love is luck,

754
00:42:57,730 --> 00:43:01,600
late night radio,

755
00:43:01,600 --> 00:43:05,270
I think we can be together.

756
00:43:11,800 --> 00:43:13,430
Special guest.

757
00:43:33,300 --> 00:43:34,000
What are you doing?

758
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:35,300
I need to use the bathroom.

759
00:43:35,300 --> 00:43:36,600
You just went.

760
00:43:36,600 --> 00:43:37,700
Let's go.

761
00:43:37,700 --> 00:43:39,630
Don't you want to find your father?

762
00:43:51,600 --> 00:43:52,870
Is this really the place?

763
00:43:52,870 --> 00:43:54,470
Let's go in and find out.

764
00:44:36,930 --> 00:44:38,000
Happy.

765
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:39,500
Very happy.

766
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:40,870
Thank you.

767
00:44:43,030 --> 00:44:44,800
Sorry for the poor hospitality.

768
00:44:44,800 --> 00:44:46,830
Mengmeng, over here!

769
00:44:46,870 --> 00:44:48,600
Mengmeng, this way.

770
00:44:50,070 --> 00:44:51,530
Mengmeng.

771
00:44:51,530 --> 00:44:53,170
Liying.

772
00:44:53,170 --> 00:44:54,600
Long time no see.

773
00:44:55,330 --> 00:44:56,470
Dad.

774
00:46:33,830 --> 00:46:35,870
Your life is a performing art,

775
00:46:35,870 --> 00:46:38,430
while mine is just a joke.

776
00:46:38,430 --> 00:46:39,000
I bet you're

777
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:41,270
not just taking kickbacks from the chicken factory.

778
00:46:41,270 --> 00:46:43,000
I agreed to everything he proposed back then.

779
00:46:43,000 --> 00:46:44,460
Do you want to scold me too?

780
00:46:45,000 --> 00:46:46,600
The recording of me and Xiao Qian,

781
00:46:46,600 --> 00:46:48,330
where did it come from?

782
00:46:48,330 --> 00:46:50,530
Some people just don't like my brother.

783
00:46:51,730 --> 00:46:54,130
Jiang Zhihao, please,

784
00:46:54,130 --> 00:46:55,430
stop singing.

785
00:46:55,430 --> 00:46:57,300
Pink Girl Concert.

786
00:46:58,500 --> 00:47:00,370
Mom, dress up nicely on Saturday.

787
00:47:00,370 --> 00:47:01,730
I'll take you on a date.
